    public interface PQBusLimit
extends AclfControlBus
    A representation of the model object 'PQ Bus Limit'. PQBusLimit for GenPQ bus. If bus voltage is outside the limit, the PQ bus is turned to a PV bus to maintain bus voltage within the limit. Object id is the same as the busId it reference to. Voltage limit is stored in the parent AclfBus object
